<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <title>Performance Assessment</title>

  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #f4f7fb;
      color: #111827;
    }

    .page {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 32px 16px;
    }

    .shell {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 980px;
    }

    .hero {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 24px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
    }

    .brand-band {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0b6fb3, #1685cf);
      padding: 36px 24px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .brand-logo {
      width: min(520px, 88%);
      max-height: 130px;
      object-fit: contain;
      display: block;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 34px;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 13px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #0b6fb3;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      font-size: clamp(30px, 5vw, 46px);
      line-height: 1.05;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .intro {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0;
      color: #4b5563;
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .section-title {
      margin: 34px 0 14px;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .card {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
      min-height: 170px;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
      transition: transform 0.18s ease, box-shadow 0.18s ease, border-color 0.18s ease;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      border-color: #0b6fb3;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 35px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
    }

    .card-label {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #6b7280;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .card-title {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 22px;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .card-copy {
      margin: 10px 0 18px;
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .card-action {
      margin-top: auto;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #111827;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .footer-actions {
      margin-top: 28px;
      padding-top: 22px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .admin-copy {
      margin: 0;
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .admin-link {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
      color: #111827;
      background: #f9fafb;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 760px) {
      .page {
        align-items: flex-start;
        padding: 16px;
      }

      .brand-band {
        padding: 28px 18px;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 24px 18px;
      }

      .cards {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .card {
        min-height: auto;
      }

      .footer-actions {
        align-items: stretch;
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .admin-link {
        width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <main class="page">
    <section class="shell">
      <div class="hero">
        <div class="brand-band">
          <img class="brand-logo" src="/zenith-logo.jpeg" alt="Zenith 360" />
        </div>

        <div class="content">
          <p class="eyebrow">Area risorse</p>
          <h1>Performance Assessment</h1>

          <p class="intro">
            Benvenuto/a nella piattaforma di assessment.
            Seleziona il questionario assegnato e procedi con la compilazione.
            Le risposte saranno utilizzate per produrre una lettura strutturata del profilo in relazione al ruolo di riferimento.
          </p>

          <h2 class="section-title">Seleziona il questionario</h2>

          <div class="cards">
            <% links.forEach(function(item) { %>
              <a class="card" href="<%= item.url %>">
                <div>
                  <p class="card-label">Questionario</p>
                  <h3 class="card-title"><%= item.label %></h3>
                  <p class="card-copy">
                    Avvia la compilazione per il ruolo <strong><%= item.label %></strong>.
                  </p>
                </div>

                <span class="card-action">Inizia assessment</span>
              </a>
            <% }) %>
          </div>

          <div class="footer-actions">
            <p class="admin-copy">
              Accesso riservato ad amministratori e consulenti autorizzati.
            </p>

            <a class="admin-link" href="/admin/login">
              Accedi all’area admin
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>